{"chapter": {"chapterId": "S1", "title": "一、执行摘要与核心拓扑", "anchor": "section-1-0", "order": 10, "blocks": [{"type": "heading", "level": 2, "text": "1.1 摘要", "anchor": "executive-summary-abstract"}, {"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "端侧大模型算力下放是AI产业从“中心集中式”向“分布式普惠”范式转移的关键进程，其商业本质在于通过技术下沉重构终端设备的价值链与定价权分配机制。这一趋势正从概念验证进入规模化应用，预计在2025-2026年深刻冲击由硬件成本、品牌溢价、软件生态和渠道结构构成的传统定价权体系。", "marks": []}]}, {"type": "engineQuote", "engine": "query", "title": "Query Agent", "blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "端侧大模型算力下放正从概念验证进入规模化应用阶段，预计2025年至2026年初将深刻影响终端市场的定价权体系。", "marks": []}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "技术层面，端侧部署已形成关键性能门槛：推理延迟需低于100ms，手机端模型内存占用需小于2GB，推理功耗需低于5W。通过模型压缩与硬件加速技术（如4bit量化、结构化剪枝），模型可大幅压缩，推理延迟显著降低，精度损失有限。", "marks": []}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "市场层面，增长迅猛。全球端侧AI市场规模预计在2029年达到1.2万亿元，年复合增长率近40%。中国市场增速更高，产业规模有望在2028年达到1.9万亿元。IDC预计2029年全球智能眼镜出货量将突破4000万台，中国信通院预计2026年AI手机和AI PC在中国市场的渗透率将分别突破50%和80%。", "marks": []}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "对定价权的核心影响呈现“K型分化”趋势：定价权向上游芯片/算法环节（如高通、联发科、苹果、英伟达）及具备全栈AI能力的终端品牌（如华为、苹果）集中。同时，商业模式正从“出售一次性硬件”向“硬件+SaaS”订阅服务转型，服务收入成为支撑硬件溢价和用户粘性的关键。", "marks": []}]}, {"type": "callout", "tone": "info", "title": "核心结论", "blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "端侧AI通过算力下沉、能力前置，让终端厂商得以摆脱对云厂商和大模型厂商的依赖，掌握用户入口与数据价值的主导权，这是对AI产业底层范式的重构，将改写过去由云厂商和操作系统平台主导的话语权规则。", "marks": []}]}]}, {"type": "heading", "level": 2, "text": "1.2 数据亮点", "anchor": "executive-summary-highlights"}, {"type": "kpiGrid", "items": [{"label": "端侧AI市场规模（2029E）", "value": "1.2万亿元", "unit": "", "delta": "年复合增长率近40%", "deltaTone": "up"}, {"label": "AI手机渗透率（2026E）", "value": ">50%", "unit": "", "delta": "中国市场", "deltaTone": "up"}, {"label": "AI PC渗透率（2026E）", "value": ">80%", "unit": "", "delta": "中国市场", "deltaTone": "up"}, {"label": "智能座舱7nm及以下芯片占比（2024）", "value": "36%", "unit": "", "delta": "预计2030年突破65%", "deltaTone": "up"}, {"label": "2026年中国手机均价涨幅", "value": "高于全球", "unit": "", "delta": "Counterpoint预测", "deltaTone": "up"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "关键性能门槛与硬件演进数据：", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}]}, {"type": "table", "rows": [{"cells": [{"blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "指标", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}]}], "align": "center"}, {"blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "关键阈值", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}]}], "align": "center"}, {"blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "说明", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}]}], "align": "center"}]}, {"cells": [{"blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "推理延迟"}]}], "align": "center"}, {"blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "<100ms"}]}], "align": "center"}, {"blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "确保实时交互体验"}]}], "align": "left"}]}, {"cells": [{"blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "内存占用（手机）"}]}], "align": "center"}, {"blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "<2GB"}]}], "align": "center"}, {"blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "7B参数模型经压缩后典型值"}]}], "align": "left"}]}, {"cells": [{"blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "推理功耗"}]}], "align": "center"}, {"blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "<5W"}]}], "align": "center"}, {"blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "平衡性能与续航"}]}], "align": "left"}]}, {"cells": [{"blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "AI PC NPU算力标准"}]}], "align": "center"}, {"blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "40 TOPS"}]}], "align": "center"}, {"blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "微软定义，英特尔/AMD/高通新品已达48-80+ TOPS"}]}], "align": "left"}]}], "caption": "端侧AI部署关键性能门槛与硬件标准", "zebra": true}, {"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "市场格局与生态数据：", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}]}, {"type": "table", "rows": [{"cells": [{"blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "维度", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}]}], "align": "center"}, {"blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "核心数据", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}]}], "align": "center"}, {"blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "与定价权关联", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}]}], "align": "center"}]}, {"cells": [{"blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "市场集中度"}]}], "align": "center"}, {"blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "2025年中国手机市场75%份额集中于华为、苹果、vivo、小米、OPPO、荣耀六家，华为重返第一"}]}], "align": "left"}, {"blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "头部厂商份额咬合紧密，竞争加剧，定价权向具备全栈能力的头部品牌集中"}]}], "align": "left"}]}, {"cells": [{"blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "生态护城河"}]}], "align": "center"}, {"blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "华为鸿蒙生态注册开发者超1000万，搭载设备数突破3600万台"}]}], "align": "left"}, {"blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "繁荣的软件生态是支撑硬件溢价、提升用户粘性与服务收入的关键"}]}], "align": "left"}]}, {"cells": [{"blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "供应链成本"}]}], "align": "center"}, {"blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "2025年存储芯片等关键元器件供应紧张、价格上涨，推高整机BOM成本"}]}], "align": "left"}, {"blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "直接导致2026年初新机起售价普遍上涨，缺乏成本转嫁能力的厂商承压"}]}], "align": "left"}]}, {"cells": [{"blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "商业模式转型"}]}], "align": "center"}, {"blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "端侧AI推动商业模式从“出售一次性硬件”向“硬件+SaaS”订阅服务转型"}]}], "align": "left"}, {"blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "定价权从硬件销售向持续的服务收入转移，改变盈利结构与用户生命周期价值"}]}], "align": "left"}]}], "caption": "市场格局、生态与成本数据对定价权的影响", "zebra": true}, {"type": "widget", "widgetId": "market-growth-chart", "widgetType": "chart.js/line", "props": {"options": {"responsive": true, "plugins": {"title": {"display": true, "text": "端侧AI市场规模增长预测（2024-2029E）"}}, "scales": {"y": {"title": {"display": true, "text": "市场规模（万亿元）"}}, "x": {"title": {"display": true, "text": "年份"}}}}}, "data": {"labels": ["2024", "2025E", "2026E", "2027E", "2028E", "2029E"], "datasets": [{"label": "全球市场规模", "data": [0.3, 0.5, 0.7, 0.9, 1.05, 1.2], "borderColor": "#1a56db", "backgroundColor": "rgba(26, 86, 219, 0.1)", "tension": 0.3}, {"label": "中国市场产业规模", "data": [0.4, 0.7, 1.1, 1.5, 1.9, null], "borderColor": "#7e3af2", "backgroundColor": "rgba(126, 58, 242, 0.1)", "tension": 0.3}]}}, "dataRef": null}, {"type": "heading", "level": 2, "text": "1.3 风险提示", "anchor": "executive-summary-risks"}, {"type": "list", "listType": "bullet", "items": [[{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "技术迭代风险：端侧AI性能标准（如NPU算力、内存带宽）快速演进，可能导致当前硬件方案迅速过时，厂商面临高昂的研发与产品迭代成本压力。", "marks": []}]}], [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "供应链成本压力：专用NPU、高带宽内存（HBM/CUBE）等关键AI组件短期内供应紧张、价格高企，直接推高终端BOM成本，侵蚀利润空间，对缺乏供应链议价能力的中小厂商构成生存威胁。", "marks": []}]}], [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "生态竞争加剧：头部厂商通过自研芯片、封闭操作系统和繁荣的应用生态构建强大护城河，导致市场“K型分化”加剧。缺乏核心技术与生态能力的厂商可能被边缘化，甚至退出市场（如魅族手机业务被传暂停）。", "marks": []}]}], [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "用户接受度与价值感知不确定性：端侧AI应用的实际用户体验和价值创造尚处早期，若无法持续提供差异化、高价值的智能服务，用户可能不愿为硬件溢价或订阅服务付费，导致商业模式转型受阻。", "marks": []}]}]]}, {"type": "callout", "tone": "warning", "title": "风险聚焦", "blocks": [{"type": "paragraph", "inlines": [{"text": "上述风险相互关联，技术迭代推高成本，成本压力削弱竞争力，生态竞争加速市场洗牌。终端厂商需在技术投入、供应链管理和生态构建之间取得艰难平衡。", "marks": []}]}]}]}}